---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="TraceLock Labs privacy policy. We collect minimal data and respect your privacy."
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-slate-100 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-slate-400">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-3">Overview</h2>
            <p>TraceLock Labs, LLC respects your privacy. This policy describes what information we collect through this website and how we use it.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="mb-3">We collect only the information you voluntarily provide through our contact form:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
              <li>Name and email address</li>
              <li>Organization name</li>
              <li>Inquiry type and message content</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>Contact form submissions are used solely to respond to your inquiry. We do not sell, share, or distribute your information to third parties.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-3">Analytics</h2>
            <p>This website does not currently use analytics tracking. No cookies are set and no personally identifiable information is collected through browsing.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-3">Data Storage</h2>
            <p>Contact form data is processed through secure, self-hosted infrastructure. We do not use third-party marketing platforms or customer data warehouses.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-3">Contact</h2>
            <p>For privacy-related questions, contact <a href="mailto:lab@tracelocklabs.com">lab@tracelocklabs.com</a>.</p>
          </div>

          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Last updated: March 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Base>
